text: Sedgwick USD 439 is a public unified school district headquartered in Sedgwick, Kansas, United States. The district includes the communities of Sedgwick, Putnam, and nearby rural areas. ==Schools== The school district currently has two schools: * Sedgwick Junior/Senior High School * R.L.
